snippet.title: The Black Eyed Peas Experience - Gameplay 4- November 2011 [DE]
snippet.description:
Hey Peabodies! In your opinion, what is the hardest dance routine in The Black Eyed Peas Experience: ""Don't Stop The Party"", ""My Style"", ""Love You Long Time"" or ""Don't Phunk With My Heart""? Tell us what your best score is!
For more information: www.facebook.com/bepexperience
